title: 服务器这个报错怎么办啊
author: zhouyitao
txt_content: [16:29:13][SEVERE][noppes.npcs.controllers.PlayerData:40] noppes.npcs.util.JsonException: Not properly incapsulated between { }: Line: 1, Pos: 0, Text:

replies.author: 粘兽
replies.txt_content:
zhouyitao 发表于 2020-2-10 23:55
[16:27:48][FINE][noppes.npcs.controllers.ScriptController:60] Fri Feb 07 16:27:48 CST 2020
[16:27: ...
1.长内容请使用论坛的"隐藏文字功能"将其折叠
2.这是解析玩家数据时产生的报错 尝试更新模组为最新版本

或到 存档/customnpcs/playerdata 删除所有玩家的数据 (切记备份)

replies.author: 粘兽
replies.txt_content:
模组customnpcs的消息
可以无视

replies.author: zhouyitao
replies.txt_content:

但是有时候直接让logs飞增。。。。将才看的时候logs文件夹里9个多g。。。
